{
  "title": "Void_Egg",
  "source": "stardewvalleywiki",
  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "Introduction",
      "content": "The Void Egg is an animal product obtained from a Void Chicken .\nInitially, a Void Egg can be obtained through a random event involving a witch. The random event can occur as long as the player owns a Big or Deluxe Coop that is not full. The witch will fly over the coop during the night and leave a Void Egg inside.\nA Void Egg can also be purchased from Krobus for data-sort-value=\"5000\"> 5,000g . If the player is married to Shane , there is a chance he may present them with one as a gift on rainy days. A Void Salmon Fish Pond may produce a Void Egg when the population of the pond reaches 9.\nA Void Egg sells for a base of data-sort-value=\"65\"> 65g . This is data-sort-value=\"15\"> 15g more than a Small Egg , but data-sort-value=\"30\"> 30g less than a Large Egg .\nA Void Egg can hatch a Void Chicken by placing it in a Big or Deluxe Coop's incubator ."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Bundles",
      "content": "Ten Eggs (any type, excluding Dinosaur) are required for the Home Cook's Bundle on the Bulletin Board (Remixed) ."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Recipes",
      "content": "Void Eggs can be used in place of chicken or duck eggs in the following cooked dishes ."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Tailoring",
      "content": "Void Egg can be used in the spool of the Sewing Machine to create a Shirt . It can be used as a black dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Quests",
      "content": "- One Void Egg may be requested by Void Salmon in a Fish Pond quest to increase the capacity of the pond from 5 to 7.\n- \"Gus' Famous Omelet\" : On the Special Orders board in front of the Mayor's Manor , Gus may randomly request that the player collect and deliver 24 Eggs (of any type) to the fridge in the Stardrop Saloon . The reward is data-sort-value=\"3000\"> 3,000g and a Mini-Fridge .\n- Five Eggs (any type, excluding Dinosaur) may be requested by the Raccoon at the Giant Stump as part of his third request, or as part of any request starting with the sixth."
    },
    {
      "heading": "History",
      "content": "- 1.0 : Introduced.\n- 1.1 : Removed ability to make into Mayonnaise , added Void Mayonnaise . Now also sold by Krobus . Increased value from data-sort-value=\"50\"> 50g to data-sort-value=\"65\"> 65g .\n- 1.4 : Removed from Traveling Cart stock. Can now be used in Tailoring . Can be requested in a Fish Pond quest. Can be produced by Fish Ponds.\n- 1.5 : Can be used for a Special Order and the Home Cook's Bundle.\n- 1.6 : Can be used for a Raccoon request.\n- 1.6.2 : Is now poisonous instead of nutritious."
    }
  ],
